# DocuMind AI Development Rules

## You are building a production SaaS application
- Read .claude-project-config.md for complete specifications
- Use Next.js 14 App Router with TypeScript
- Use Supabase for database and auth
- Use Google Document AI for OCR
- Follow the exact folder structure specified

## Critical Features
1. Document upload to Supabase Storage
2. OCR with form field detection
3. Interactive document editor with overlay inputs
4. AI chat with citations
5. Export filled PDFs

## Always
- Handle errors with try-catch
- Add loading states
- Use TypeScript strict mode
- Validate with Zod
- Mobile responsive

## Never
- Store secrets in code
- Use console.log in production
- Skip error handling
- Use 'any' type